sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Invited User
    participant FE as Web Frontend
    participant API as InvitationController
    participant S as InvitationApplicationService
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant C as CredentialService
    participant SS as SessionStore/Redis
    participant A as Audit Platform

    U->>FE: open /accept-invite?userId&token
    FE->>API: POST /invitations/validate {userId, rawToken}
    API->>S: validateInvitation()
    S->>S: tokenHash = hash(rawToken)
    S->>DB: find invitation by tenant + userId + tokenHash
    alt invitation missing, revoked, accepted, expired, or user ineligible
        DB-->>S: invalid state
        S->>A: invitation.invalid.used (no token data)
        S-->>API: generic contact-admin error
        API-->>FE: AUTH_INVITATION_INVALID-class response
        FE-->>U: link invalid, contact administrator
    else valid PENDING invitation
        DB-->>S: invitation + user
        S-->>API: validation grant or validated context
        API-->>FE: allow password setup screen
        U->>FE: submit new password
        FE->>API: POST /invitations/accept {userId, rawToken, password}
        API->>S: acceptInvitation()
        S->>DB: BEGIN
        S->>DB: SELECT invitation FOR UPDATE by userId + tokenHash
        S->>C: validate policy and Argon2id hash password
        C-->>S: passwordHash
        S->>DB: UPSERT Credential(ACTIVE)
        S->>DB: Invitation -> ACCEPTED
        S->>DB: User -> ACTIVE, securityVersion++
        S->>DB: COMMIT
        S->>SS: revoke any stale/restricted sessions
        S->>A: invitation.accepted + password.setup.via.invitation
        S-->>API: success
        API-->>FE: onboarding completed
        FE-->>U: redirect to login
    end
